open [table|all] | Show current firewall rules in a readable format.
flush <table> | Remove all rules from a specific table.
flush all | Remove all rules from all tables.
backup | save | Create a backup of the firewall configuration.
restore | Restore firewall rules from a backup.
raw <iptables cmd> | Execute native iptables commands directly.
.TE

